{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":404,"text":"I've noticed something interesting\nabout society and culture."},{"time":3310,"text":"Everything risky requires a license."},{"time":5892,"text":"So, learning to drive,\nowning a gun, getting married."},{"time":11177,"text":"There's a certain --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12535,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":14859,"text":"That's true in everything risky,\nexcept technology."},{"time":18604,"text":"For some reason,\nthere's no standard syllabus,"},{"time":20963,"text":"there's no basic course."},{"time":22953,"text":"They just sort of give you your computer\nand then kick you out of the nest."},{"time":26596,"text":"You're supposed to learn\nthis stuff -- how?"},{"time":28897,"text":"Just by osmosis."},{"time":30148,"text":"Nobody ever sits down and tells you,\n\"This is how it works.\""},{"time":33064,"text":"So today I'm going to tell you ten things"},{"time":36041,"text":"that you thought everybody knew,\nbut it turns out they don't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39431,"text":"First of all, on the web,\nif you want to scroll down,"},{"time":42241,"text":"don't pick up the mouse\nand use the scroll bar."},{"time":44506,"text":"That's a terrible waste of time."},{"time":46057,"text":"Do that only if you're paid by the hour."},{"time":48121,"text":"Instead, hit the space bar."},{"time":50022,"text":"The space bar scrolls down one page."},{"time":53885,"text":"Hold down the Shift key\nto scroll back up again."},{"time":56790,"text":"So, space bar to scroll down one page;\nworks in every browser,"},{"time":59726,"text":"in every kind of computer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61003,"text":"Also on the web, when you're filling in\none of these forms like your addresses,"},{"time":64749,"text":"I assume you know\nthat you can hit the Tab key"},{"time":66982,"text":"to jump from box to box to box."},{"time":68585,"text":"But what about the pop-up menu\nwhere you put in your state?"},{"time":71755,"text":"Don't open the pop-up menu."},{"time":73684,"text":"That's a terrible waste of calories."},{"time":75572,"text":"Type the first letter of your state\nover and over and over."},{"time":79166,"text":"So if you want Connecticut, go, C, C, C."},{"time":81418,"text":"If you want Texas, go T, T,\nand you jump right to that thing"},{"time":84854,"text":"without even opening the pop-up menu."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87278,"text":"Also on the web,\nwhen the text is too small,"},{"time":90186,"text":"what you do is hold down the Control key\nand hit plus, plus, plus."},{"time":93710,"text":"You make the text larger with each tap."},{"time":96917,"text":"Works on every computer,\nevery web browser,"},{"time":99009,"text":"or minus, minus, to get smaller again."},{"time":101003,"text":"If you're on the Mac,\nit might be Command instead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103593,"text":"When you're typing\non your Blackberry, Android, iPhone,"},{"time":107457,"text":"don't bother switching layouts\nto the punctuation layout"},{"time":110743,"text":"to hit the period and then a space,"},{"time":112601,"text":"then try to capitalize the next letter."},{"time":114530,"text":"Just hit the space bar twice."},{"time":116557,"text":"The phone puts the period,\nthe space, and the capital for you."},{"time":120531,"text":"Go space, space."},{"time":121750,"text":"It is totally amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123938,"text":"Also when it comes\nto cell phones, on all phones,"},{"time":126976,"text":"if you want to redial\nsomebody that you've dialed before,"},{"time":130586,"text":"all you have to do is hit the call button,"},{"time":133131,"text":"and it puts the last phone number\ninto the box for you,"},{"time":136726,"text":"and at that point you can hit\ncall again to actually dial it."},{"time":139881,"text":"No need to go to the recent calls list\nif you're trying to call somebody"},{"time":143429,"text":"just hit the call button again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144944,"text":"Something that drives me crazy:"},{"time":146451,"text":"When I call you and leave a message\non your voice mail,"},{"time":149070,"text":"I hear you saying, \"Leave a message,\""},{"time":150864,"text":"and then I get these 15 seconds\nof freaking instructions,"},{"time":154245,"text":"like we haven't had\nanswering machines for 45 years!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":157933,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":161621,"text":"I'm not bitter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163098,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164129,"text":"So it turns out\nthere's a keyboard shortcut"},{"time":166365,"text":"that lets you jump directly\nto the beep like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168747,"text":"Phone: At the tone, please..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170358,"text":"(Beep)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":171383,"text":"David Pogue: Unfortunately,\nthe carriers didn't adopt"},{"time":173897,"text":"the same keystroke,\nso it's different by carrier,"},{"time":176362,"text":"so it devolves upon you\nto learn the keystroke"},{"time":179427,"text":"for the person you're calling."},{"time":182058,"text":"I didn't say these were going\nto be perfect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184656,"text":"So most of you think of Google"},{"time":186330,"text":"as something that lets you\nlook up a web page,"},{"time":188606,"text":"but it is also a dictionary."},{"time":190000,"text":"Type the word \"define\"\nand the word you want to know."},{"time":192616,"text":"You don't even have to click anything."},{"time":194465,"text":"There's the definition as you type."},{"time":196545,"text":"It's also a complete FAA database."},{"time":198600,"text":"Type the name of the airline\nand the flight."},{"time":200708,"text":"It shows you where the flight is,\nthe gate, the terminal,"},{"time":203431,"text":"how long until it lands."},{"time":204741,"text":"You don't need an app."},{"time":206176,"text":"It's also unit and currency conversion."},{"time":208167,"text":"Again, you don't have to click\none of the results."},{"time":210814,"text":"Just type it into the box,\nand there's your answer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213443,"text":"While we're talking about text --"},{"time":215945,"text":"When you want to highlight --"},{"time":218712,"text":"this is just an example --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":220102,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221990,"text":"When you want to highlight a word,"},{"time":224273,"text":"please don't waste your life\ndragging across it"},{"time":227267,"text":"with the mouse like a newbie."},{"time":228701,"text":"Double click the word."},{"time":230359,"text":"Watch \"200\" -- I go double-click,"},{"time":232044,"text":"it neatly selects just that word."},{"time":233777,"text":"Also, don't delete\nwhat you've highlighted."},{"time":236518,"text":"You can just type over it."},{"time":237915,"text":"This is in every program."},{"time":239469,"text":"Also, you can go double-click, drag,"},{"time":241484,"text":"to highlight in one-word\nincrements as you drag."},{"time":244390,"text":"Much more precise."},{"time":245654,"text":"Again, don't bother deleting."},{"time":247513,"text":"Just type over it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248843,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252575,"text":"Shutter lag is the time\nbetween your pressing the shutter button"},{"time":256080,"text":"and the moment the camera actually snaps."},{"time":258438,"text":"It's extremely frustrating\non any camera under $1,000."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261406,"text":"(Camera click)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":263040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":266383,"text":"So, that's because the camera needs time\nto calculate the focus and exposure,"},{"time":270381,"text":"but if you pre-focus with a half-press,"},{"time":273266,"text":"leave your finger down --"},{"time":275056,"text":"no shutter lag!"},{"time":277309,"text":"You get it every time."},{"time":279438,"text":"I've just turned your $50 camera\ninto a $1,000 camera with that trick."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283646,"text":"And finally, it often happens\nthat you're giving a talk,"},{"time":286979,"text":"and for some reason,\nthe audience is looking at the slide"},{"time":290035,"text":"instead of at you!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291317,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":293715,"text":"So when that happens --\nthis works in Keynote, PowerPoint,"},{"time":296642,"text":"it works in every program\n-- all you do is hit the letter B key,"},{"time":299677,"text":"B for blackout, to black out the slide,\nmake everybody look at you,"},{"time":303254,"text":"and then when you're ready\nto go on, you hit B again,"},{"time":305757,"text":"and if you're really on a roll,\nyou can hit the W key for \"whiteout,\""},{"time":310244,"text":"and you white out the slide,"},{"time":311979,"text":"and then you can hit W again\nto un-blank it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314644,"text":"So I know I went super fast."},{"time":316278,"text":"If you missed anything, I'll be happy\nto send you the list of these tips."},{"time":319746,"text":"In the meantime, congratulations."},{"time":321345,"text":"You all get your California\nTechnology License."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323802,"text":"Have a great day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325038,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}